Are these libraries stranded?

Yes, these libraries are both stranded. The results of the reverse HTseq runs are 79.12% and 84.42% for the 11_2H_both_S9_L008 and 29_4E_fox_S21_L008 libraries respectively. Comparatively, the results of the forward stranded HTseq run only have 3.19% and 3.93% for the 11_2H_both_S9_L008 and 29_4E_fox_S21_L008 libraries respectively. The higher alignment numbers for the reverse run indicate that the reverse stranded R2 file aligned better that the Forward R1 file.
